<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>El More — Вход в админку</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300;1,400&family=Manrope:wght@300;400;500&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/admin/static/admin.css" />
</head>
<body class="login-body">
  <div class="login-grain"></div>
  <div class="login-wrap">
    <div class="login-left">
      <div class="login-mark">El<i>&nbsp;More</i></div>
      <div class="login-sub">Hôtel · Maison de Repos</div>
      <div class="login-cap">— Panneau d'administration · accès réservé</div>
    </div>
    <form class="login-form" method="POST" action="/admin/login">
      <div class="login-eyebrow">— Connexion · MMXXVI</div>
      <h1 class="login-title">Добро<br/><em>пожаловать.</em></h1>
      <p class="login-desc">Войдите, чтобы редактировать содержимое сайта El More.</p>

      <label class="login-field">
        <span>Пароль</span>
        <input type="password" name="password" required autofocus placeholder="••••••••" />
      </label>

      <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="login-err"><span class="dot"></span><%= error %></div>
      <% } %>

      <button type="submit" class="login-btn">
        <span class="dot"></span>Войти<span class="dot"></span>
      </button>

      <a href="/" class="login-back">← Вернуться на сайт</a>
    </form>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
